{"route":{"route":"/posts/1754556687621/","outputPath":"posts/1754556687621/index.html","kind":"post","title":"RustでTelegram BotをLambdaにデプロイする","language":"ja","params":{"abbrlink":"1754556687621"}},"description":"Telegram BotにはサーバーとWebhookの二つの立ち上げる方法があります。Lambdaはサーバーレスだから、今回はWebhookで使用します。 最初はCargoで新たなプロジェクトを作ります。 必要な依存を追加します。 zigをインストール Telegramのコマンドを宣言します ご確認ください Teleg","post":{"kind":"post","sourcePath":"source/_posts/RustでTelegram-BotをLambdaにデプロイする/doc.md","route":"/posts/1754556687621/","abbrlink":"1754556687621","title":"RustでTelegram BotをLambdaにデプロイする","date":"2025-08-07 16:51:27","updated":"2025-08-07 16:51:27","tags":["Telegram","Telegram Bot","Rust","Cargo","Teloxide","Lambda"],"categories":["Rust","Lambda","Telegram"],"language":"ja","htmlLang":"ja","locale":"ja_JP","textDirection":"ltr","dateLocale":"ja-JP","excerptMarkdown":"","excerptHtml":"","bodyMarkdown":"","bodyHtml":"<p>Telegram BotにはサーバーとWebhookの二つの立ち上げる方法があります。Lambdaはサーバーレスだから、今回はWebhookで使用します。</p>\n<p>最初はCargoで新たなプロジェクトを作ります。</p>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">cargo new telegram-bot</span></span></code></pre>\n<p>必要な依存を追加します。</p>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">crgo add aws_lambda_events <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">base64</span> lambda_runtime serde_json serde teloxide-macros tokio teloxide cargo-lambda</span></span></code></pre>\n<p>zigをインストール</p>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\"># macos</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">2</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">brew install zig</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">3</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\"># lambda cliでzigのインストール方法を出力して</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">4</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">cargo lambda system --install-zig</span></span></code></pre>\n<p>Telegramのコマンドを宣言します</p>\n<!--チェックしてください　<==>　ご確認ください-->\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-rust\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-meta\">#[derive(BotCommands, PartialEq, Clone, Debug)]</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">2</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\">// いろんなパラメータに対応しています。公式ドキュメントをチェックしてください。</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">3</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-meta\">#[command(</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">4</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    rename_rule = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;lowercase&quot;</span>,</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">5</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    description = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;These commands are supported:&quot;</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">6</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">)]</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">7</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">pub</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">enum</span> <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Command</span> {</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">8</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    <span class=\"hljs-meta\">#[command(description = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;get current user id&quot;</span>)]</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">9</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    UserID,</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">10</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">}</span></span></code></pre>\n<p>Telegramの処理関数を定義します</p>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-rust\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">pub</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">async</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">fn</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">answer</span>(</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">2</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    bot: teloxide::prelude::Bot,</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">3</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    msg: Message,</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">4</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    cmd: Command,</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">5</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">) <span class=\"hljs-punctuation\">-&gt;</span> <span class=\"hljs-type\">Result</span>&lt;(), RequestError&gt; {</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">6</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> <span class=\"hljs-variable\">reply</span> = <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">match</span> cmd {</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">7</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">        Command::UserID =&gt; <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">format!</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;your id is: {}&quot;</span>, from_user).<span class=\"hljs-title function_ invoke__\">to_string</span>(),</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">8</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    }</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">9</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> </span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">10</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// 返事を送信し</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">11</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    bot.<span class=\"hljs-title function_ invoke__\">send_message</span>(msg.chat.id, v)</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">12</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">        .<span class=\"hljs-title function_ invoke__\">reply_parameters</span>(ReplyParameters::<span class=\"hljs-title function_ invoke__\">new</span>(msg.id))</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">13</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">        .<span class=\"hljs-title function_ invoke__\">parse_mode</span>(teloxide::types::ParseMode::MarkdownV2)</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">14</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">        .<span class=\"hljs-title function_ invoke__\">disable_link_preview</span>(<span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>)</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">15</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">        .<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">await</span>?;</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">16</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> </span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">17</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    <span class=\"hljs-title function_ invoke__\">Ok</span>(())</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">18</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">}</span></span></code></pre>\n<p>Telegramのルートを定義します</p>\n<p>ここはちょっと難しいかもしれません</p>\n<ul>\n<li><code>Update::filter_message()</code>は一般的なメッセージ</li>\n<li><code>Update::filter_edited_message()</code>は更新したメッセージ</li>\n<li>他の種類のメッセージは<a href=\"https://docs.rs/teloxide/latest/teloxide/dispatching/trait.UpdateFilterExt.html\">trait.UpdateFilterExt</a>にご確認ください。</li>\n</ul>\n<p><code>filter_command::&lt;Command&gt;()</code>はCommandによってメッセージをフィルターする。　　<br>\n例えば<code>filter_command</code>を削除して<code>dptree::entry().endpoint(answer)</code>になったら、これはすべてのメッセージをマッチする。</p>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-rust\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">pub</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">fn</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">handler</span>() <span class=\"hljs-punctuation\">-&gt;</span> Handler&lt;<span class=\"hljs-symbol\">&#x27;static</span>, <span class=\"hljs-type\">Result</span>&lt;(), RequestError&gt;, DpHandlerDescription&gt; {</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">2</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">return</span> dptree::<span class=\"hljs-title function_ invoke__\">entry</span>()</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">3</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">        .<span class=\"hljs-title function_ invoke__\">branch</span>(</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">4</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">            Update::<span class=\"hljs-title function_ invoke__\">filter_message</span>()</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">5</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">                .<span class=\"hljs-title function_ invoke__\">branch</span>(dptree::<span class=\"hljs-title function_ invoke__\">entry</span>().filter_command::&lt;Command&gt;().<span class=\"hljs-title function_ invoke__\">endpoint</span>(answer)),</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">6</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">        )</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">7</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">        .<span class=\"hljs-title function_ invoke__\">branch</span>(</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">8</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">            Update::<span class=\"hljs-title function_ invoke__\">filter_edited_message</span>()</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">9</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">                .<span class=\"hljs-title function_ invoke__\">branch</span>(dptree::<span class=\"hljs-title function_ invoke__\">entry</span>().filter_command::&lt;Command&gt;().<span class=\"hljs-title function_ invoke__\">endpoint</span>(answer)),</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">10</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">        );</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">11</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">}</span></span></code></pre>\n<p>Telegram Botサーバーなら次のコードで実行できます。Lambdaには他の方法を使います。</p>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-rust\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">pub</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">struct</span> <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">TErrorHandler</span> {}</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">2</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> </span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">3</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">impl</span> <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ErrorHandler</span>&lt;RequestError&gt; <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for</span> <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">TErrorHandler</span> {</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">4</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">fn</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">handle_error</span>(<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">self</span>: std::sync::Arc&lt;<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">Self</span>&gt;, error: RequestError) <span class=\"hljs-punctuation\">-&gt;</span> BoxFuture&lt;<span class=\"hljs-symbol\">&#x27;static</span>, ()&gt; {</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">5</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">        <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">println!</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;error: {}&quot;</span>, error);</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">6</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">        <span class=\"hljs-type\">Box</span>::<span class=\"hljs-title function_ invoke__\">pin</span>(<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">async</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">move</span> {})</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">7</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    }</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">8</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">}</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">9</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> </span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">10</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">pub</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">async</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">fn</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">run_bot</span>() <span class=\"hljs-punctuation\">-&gt;</span> Dispatcher&lt;Bot, RequestError, DefaultKey&gt; {</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">11</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> <span class=\"hljs-variable\">bot</span> = Bot::<span class=\"hljs-title function_ invoke__\">from_env</span>();</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">12</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> </span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">13</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    bot.<span class=\"hljs-title function_ invoke__\">set_my_commands</span>(Command::<span class=\"hljs-title function_ invoke__\">bot_commands</span>())</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">14</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">        .<span class=\"hljs-title function_ invoke__\">send</span>()</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">15</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">        .<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">await</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">16</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">        .<span class=\"hljs-title function_ invoke__\">unwrap</span>();</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">17</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> </span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">18</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> <span class=\"hljs-variable\">handler</span> = <span class=\"hljs-title function_ invoke__\">handler</span>();</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">19</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> </span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">20</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> </span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">21</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> <span class=\"hljs-variable\">dispatcher</span>: Dispatcher&lt;Bot, RequestError, DefaultKey&gt; = Dispatcher::<span class=\"hljs-title function_ invoke__\">builder</span>(bot, handler)</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">22</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">        .<span class=\"hljs-title function_ invoke__\">enable_ctrlc_handler</span>()</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">23</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">        .<span class=\"hljs-title function_ invoke__\">error_handler</span>(Arc::<span class=\"hljs-title function_ invoke__\">new</span>(TErrorHandler {}))</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">24</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">        .<span class=\"hljs-title function_ invoke__\">build</span>();</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">25</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> </span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">26</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">return</span> dispatcher;</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria