span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">Token</span>&gt;</span></span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">2</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"></span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>ビルド</p>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">cargo lambda build --release --bin lambda</span></span></code></pre>\n<p>デプロイ</p>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">cargo lambda deploy --binary-name lambda hj-telegram-bot</span></span></code></pre>\n<p>Webhookを登録します</p>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">curl https://&lt;<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> url&gt;/tgbot/register</span></span></code></pre>\n<p>これで完成しました。<br>\nTelegram Botに<code>/userid</code>を送信してテストしましょう。</p>\n","rawMarkdown":"","plainText":"","toc":[],"slugForSearch":"1754556687621","comments":true,"math":false,"mermaid":false}}